    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"people caring\" doesnt change the math tho. the universe is infinite and cold, and we are just temporary chemical reactions. even if people care, it doesnt make the struggle any less pointless in the long run. if nothing lasts, and nothing really matters, why even put in the effort to stay? it feels like we're just dragging ourselves through a theater of the absurd for no reason.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
